
Grid Game

Objects
Player Character - 
	keypad movement - 4 directional
	Health
	z - interact/attack
	x - check items

Environment - 
Tree
Wall
Grass (walkable)
Path (walkable)
Floor (walkable)
Road (walkable)

Interactive -
Door - Open w or w/o item
Chest - Get Item
NPC - Show message//get item
Sign - Show message
Heart - Heal
Enemy - Random Movement// Collision = Damage
Enemy Projectile - Linear Movement// Collision = Damage

Other:
Non Scrolling - Reload each screen as needed
Objective: Basic Adventure Game